727867f-a.title: Queens: Range Street - 87th Avenue
727867f-a.text:
Range Street, adjoining the N.E. corner of 87th Avenue,
Creedmoor, showing the Creedmoor Hose Company's fire house.
Creedmoor is an old village in the southeastern corner of
Flushing, near the Jamaica town line.
P. L. Sperr  June 6, 1927
